@page "/privacy"

<PageContainer MaxWidth="narrow">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p class="mt-6 leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
        This tool is built for local diagnostics. We never store, share, or sell your uploaded data.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 space-y-4 leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
        <p>
            Your CSV file is processed to generate a diagnostic report. The report token lets you view results and
            download an errors file.
        </p>
        <p>
            We use Google Analytics to collect anonymous usage statistics (page views and feature usage).
            We do not store uploaded CSV files or their contents.
        </p>
        <p>
            Telemetry is limited to operational metrics (e.g., counts and sizes) to help improve reliability.
        </p>
    </div>
</PageContainer>
